<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="First Web Page" content="First Web Page">

    <title>First Web Page</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <h1>Welcome to My First Web Page</h1>
        </header>
        <nav>
            <a href="#home">Home</a>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
        <main>
            <h2>About This Page</h2>
            <p>This is a simple web page created as part of a learning exercise. It includes basic HTML structure adding styling, and navigation along with elements i have learned. </p>
        <section>
            <h2>Topics Covered</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>HTML Structure</li>
                <li>Meta Tags</li>
                <li>Headings, Paragraphs, Spans and Divs</li>
                <li>List</li>
                <li>Tables</li>
                <li>Forms</li>
                </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
        <h2>Embedding a YouTube Video</h2>
        <iframe
        width="600"
        height="400"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=al9ITeP4fUA" frameborder="0"
        title= "My first video"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
        allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2> Student Scores</h2>
            <table border="1">
                <tr>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <th>Score</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Alice</td>
                    <td>85</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Bob</td>
                    <td>90</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Gina</td>
                    <td>78</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Sign Up Form</h2>
            <form action="/submit" method="post">
               <br>
        <label for="name">Name:</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" required />
        <br />

        <label for="email">Email:</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" required />
        <br />

        <label for="password">Password:</label>
        <input type="password" id="password" required>
        <br />
        <input type="submit" value="Submit">
        <br>
        <label for="country">Country:</label>
        <select id="country" name="country">
            <option value="us">United States</option>
            <option value="ca">Canada</option>
            <option value="uk">United Kingdom</option>
            </select>
            <br />
            <br />
            <button type="submit">Sign Up</button>
            </form>
        </main>
        <footer>
            &copy; 2026 My First Web Page
        </footer>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #1e31da;
            color: #1a0c0c;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        nav {
            background-color: #444;
            overflow: hidden;
            
        }
        nav a {
            float: left;
            display: block;
            color: #2e4eff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #dddddddc;
            color: black;
        }
        main {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #e634dd;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</html>